Placement Aptitude Training (Teacher Mode)

1️⃣ VERBAL ABILITY – READING COMPREHENSION (RC)

This is one of the most important sections in placements 🔥
(Asked in almost every company)

🔹 A. WHAT IS RC?

👉 You are given a passage
👉 Then asked questions based on it

🔹 B. HOW TO SOLVE RC (VERY IMPORTANT)

Follow this method:

1️⃣ Read questions first (quickly)
2️⃣ Then read passage carefully
3️⃣ Identify:

Main idea
Keywords
Tone
🔹 C. TYPES OF QUESTIONS
Main idea
Detail-based
Inference
Vocabulary
🔹 D. PASSAGE EXAMPLE

“Technology has transformed modern life. It has improved communication, increased productivity, and made information easily accessible. However, excessive use of technology can lead to reduced physical activity and social interaction.”

🔹 Example Questions
What is the main idea?
👉 Technology has both benefits and drawbacks
What is a disadvantage?
👉 Reduced physical activity
🔹 E. IMPORTANT STRATEGY

❌ Don’t assume
✅ Answer only from passage

🔹 F. COMMON MISTAKES
Reading too fast
Guessing answers
Ignoring keywords
📝 PRACTICE QUESTIONS

Read and answer:

“Education plays a vital role in personal development. It enhances knowledge, improves skills, and creates opportunities. Without education, growth becomes limited.”

What is the main idea?
What does education improve?
What happens without education?
Find a synonym of “enhances”
What is the tone of passage?
